OL,3,CDiving platform closed permanently
OL,4,Cover serious injury concerns
OL,6,FA popular diving platform in Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas been permanently closed due to
OL,8,Fconcerns over the increased chance of
OL,9,Fserious injury.
OL,11,FThe outdoor Ladies' Pool has been
OL,12,Fwelcoming swimmers for more than 150
OL,13,Fyears but a prohibition notice has now
OL,14,Fbeen served on the States of Guernsey
OL,15,Ffollowing a risk assessment by the
OL,16,FHealth and Safety Executive.
