OL,3,CDiving platform closed permanently
OL,4,Cover serious injury concerns
OL,6,FIt was called in after reports of near
OL,7,Fmisses involving the platform and has
OL,8,Fconcluded that the water depth of 2-
OL,9,F2.75 metres is unsafe as it falls
OL,10,Fbelow the minimum 3.2-metre clearance
OL,11,Frequired by World Aquatics and British
OL,12,FStandards.
OL,14,FTo reopen the platform, the States
OL,15,Fsays it would need to increase the
OL,16,Fdepth of the pool and eliminate leaks,
OL,17,Fwhich is estimated to cost around #1
OL,18,Fmillion.
