OL,3,CDiving platform closed permanently
OL,4,Cover serious injury concerns
OL,6,FEven if the height of the platform was
OL,7,Flowered, under regulations there would
OL,8,Fstill need to be a separate area for
OL,9,Fdiving which is supervised at all
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,12,FThe States adds this is not a likely
OL,13,Foption due to the cost of hiring extra
OL,14,Fstaff.
