OL,3,CDiving platform closed permanently
OL,4,Cover serious injury concerns
OL,6,FRobin Gonard, Chief Officer of the
OL,7,FHealth and Safety Executive, explains:
OL,8,F"While we recognise it has been a
OL,9,Ffeature of the Ladies' Pool for
OL,10,Fdecades, international safety
OL,11,Fstandards have naturally developed as
OL,12,Frisk management has become more
OL,13,Fprevalent in modern times.
OL,15,F"In light of the assessment we carried
OL,16,Fout, our decision was that immediate
OL,17,Faction needs to be taken to ensure
OL,18,Fcompliance with modern safety
OL,19,Fstandards to protect members of our
OL,20,Fcommunity by avoiding the risk of
OL,21,Fserious injury or worse."
